{"tid":1321590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華爾街日報:美製造商將供應鏈撤出中國","createTime":"2019-07-15T17:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T17:34:18.000Z","uid":30561,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"11f5b0e1730da178a2d51b39463b22dcc0881c1d","tid":1321590,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"華爾街日報:美製造商將供應鏈撤出中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Stock/M.1563156171.A.808.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FStock%2FM.1563156171.A.808.html&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=6916ac66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Stock/M.1563156171.A.808.html</a><br />\n<br />\n1.原文連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/yy3dss88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fyy3dss88&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=19129200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/yy3dss88</a><br />\n2.原文內容：<br />\nFacts:<br />\n1.美、中貿易戰邁入第二年，美國製造商正持續將產線移出中國。<br />\nReasons to Believe<br />\n (1)Crocs:2020年在中國生產的鞋子將降至10%以下<br />\n   Yeti beer coolers:將把大部分產線在今年底移出中國<br />\n   iRobot:將在馬來西亞成立新的Roomba吸塵器產線<br />\n   GoPro相機等正將產線移出中國以規避高達25%的關稅。Apple也正在考慮將組裝的產線<br />\n搬離中國。<br />\n (2)傢俱製造商Lovesac正將中國60%的產線撤出中國，CEO Shawn Nelson表示公司正積極<br />\n的至越南生產，Nelson表示預計到2020年底將在中國停產。<br />\n2.這波全球供應鏈的重組乃基於美、中間貿易談判預期將持續，而建立新的產線需要時間<br />\n及精力，因此現在便需採取行動，而這波加速撤離的行動是今年5月稅率從10%調升至25%<br />\n。<br />\n3.美國自中國進口產品截至5月年減12%，這是自金融海嘯以來最大減幅。<br />\n4.受惠國家:越南、印度、台灣、馬來西亞，主要是這些國家生產成本相對低。美國今年<br />\n至越南進口金額預計達648億美元，年增36%。<br />\n<br />\n3.心得/評論：<br />\n有國家受惠自然有國家受傷，企業也是。目前Trump在跟中國貿易deal上跟對北韓的態度<br />\n有點轉變成不急了，特別是7月之後他分別講了不急著有deal，若在看到Mnuchin發表對雙<br />\n方談判有樂觀態度的言論時，投資人應該會越來越無感才是。"},{"pid":"0828aaefefef83d0acc709a3b5e7eef64dbf2b26","tid":1321590,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n========================="},{"pid":"a9a80777ef6cddcf6a737f75998c87fe25eff9ab","tid":1321590,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:07:23.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre><br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c23d0b6c6ff2e7751b1d8f56ab2bc8813047be05","tid":1321590,"uid":238613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"抵死啦 中國人 <br />\n肯定又驚啲中國人偷技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076b1e82b5ebfbd4ed93419a604ca23da78ff9fa","tid":1321590,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"美國會唔會打算同金正日deal好之後 叫啲廠搬去北韓 進一步打擊中國？"},{"pid":"634c6504fc2ee9f4b2483509f7e3f942b2395fd6","tid":1321590,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:34:18.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321643</a>"}]}